Description: Joining Jeffrey today is return guest, Mads Torgersen! Mads is the Lead Designer of the C# language and has been at Microsoft for 16 years. Prior to this, Mads was a professor and contributed to a language starting with J. Title: How to Disable GitHub Actions in a Forked Project
Description: Some GitHub repositories have GitHub Actions with helpful automation. Because actions are stored in the .github folder within a codebase, they come over along with any forks that are created. In many cases, this could be really helpful, as you get a great level of automation out of the box.
